    "Then, we discuss their diverse applications in both scholarly and general settings.",
    "This review establishes a foundation for our investigation, which aims to understand the sociolinguistic profiles of LLMs.",
    "Recent advances in transformer-based architectures have enabled the development of LLMs that can generate impressively human-like text and respond to complex questions and prompts (Brown et al, 2020).",
    "Models like OpenAI's GPT-3.5 and GPT-4 are trained on massive textual corpora extracted from the internet, allowing them to learn the statistical patterns of language and generate coherent new text given a prompt.",
